{"assetKey":"Game_AdditionalContents_AdvancedLocomotionV4_CharacterAssets_MannequinSkeleton_Editor","graph":"AnimGraph","nodeGuid":"24FCD1E24A09A109B8AA6082357E142C","class":"EdGraphNode_Comment","title":"This AnimBP can be used in the editor as a Post Process Instance to modify an animation, which can then be recorded / exported as a new asset. Below is the logic I used on the M4A1 Run and Sprint animations so that it plays only on the arms, which I then exported as a new asset for use in the main AnimBP.\r\n\r\nThis is a technique I used as a timesaver, so I didnt have to further edit the animation in maya.","comment":"This AnimBP can be used in the editor as a Post Process Instance to modify an animation, which can then be recorded / exported as a new asset. Below is the logic I used on the M4A1 Run and Sprint animations so that it plays only on the arms, which I then exported as a new asset for use in the main AnimBP.\r\n\r\nThis is a technique I used as a timesaver, so I didnt have to further edit the animation in maya.","x":-1024,"y":-256,"memberName":"","functionName":"","variableName":"","targetClass":"","isPure":false,"pins":[],"terms":["EdGraphNode_Comment"]}
